  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction à GNOME System Monitor</title>

    <para>
      Le paquet <application>GNOME System Monitor</application> contient le
remplaçant <application>GNOME</application> de <command>gtop</command>.
    </para>

    &lfs112_checked;

